Exclusive Golf
Membership Plans
GOLF
MEMBERSHIP
All golf memberships enjoy the use of all amenities at Club Adena with preferred tee time reservations.
YOUNG
EXECUTIVE GOLF
MEMBERSHIP
Members under 40 years of age will enjoy the use of all facilities at Club Adena including the following:
Spa and Swimming Pool
Tennis & Pickleball Courts
Lounge Bar
Dining Room
18 Hole Golf Course
SOCIAL
MEMBERSHIP
Members will enjoy all amenities on the property including:
Spa and Swimming Pool
Tennis & Pickleball Courts
Lounge Bar
Dining Room
CORPORATE GOLF
MEMBERSHIP
Corporate memberships will be entitled to an allowance of up to four title members and will enjoy the use of the following amenities
Spa and Swimming Pool
Tennis & Pickleball Courts
Lounge Bar
Dining Room
NATIONAL GOLF
MEMBERSHIP
National membership must live 75 miles from the club and will enjoy the use of the following amenities
Spa and Swimming Pool
Tennis & Pickleball Courts
Lounge Bar
Dining Room
